    "body": "Of course, it's great when the simple method does work. But there's a significant fraction of cases where it won't, so we can't offer it as something that works for everyone. But for what it's worth, the 'Quickstart' section of the [installation instructions](http://ipython.org/ipython-doc/stable/install/install.html#quickstart) does give that simple method.\n"
  },
